    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Animal Friendship</strong> (Level 1 Enchantment)</p><p>This spell lets you convince a beast that you mean it no harm. Choose a beast that you can see within range. It must see and hear you. If the beast's Intelligence is 4 or higher, the spell fails. Otherwise, the beast must succeed on a wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you for the spell's duration. If you or one of your companions harms the target, the spells ends.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A morsel of food.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> 24 hours</p><p><em>Classes: Bard, Druid, Ranger</em></p>",
